[Nouns] discount, abatement, concession, reduction, depreciation, allowance; qualification, set-off, drawback, poundage, agio, percentage; rebate, rebatement; backwardation, contango; salvage; tare and tret.
[Verbs] discount, bate; abate, rebate; reduce, take off, allow, give, make allowance; tax.
[Adjectives] discounting
[Adverbs] at a discount, below par.
